====Pokémon Diamond and Pearl Adventure!====
{{main|Hareta}}
Hareta from [[Pokémon Diamond and Pearl Adventure!]] is based on Lucas. He's a dimwitted, headstrong boy who was partially raised in the wild after [[Kaisei|his father]] left him in [[Professor Rowan]]'s care as a small child, causing him to constantly misunderstand how some everyday things, like [[Poké Ball]]s or [[Bicycle|bikes]], are supposed to be used.
